   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00043-B-00003-000-00021"/>Herrn D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb168940" type="place">XVIII Spöttelgasse 7</rs></hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><p rend="center"><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00043-B-00003-000-00022"/><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb44758">Anna Amalia</rs> und ihre Begleiter in der <rs type="place" ref="#pmb44762">Villa d’Este</rs>. <rs ref="#pmb4996" type="person">Herder</rs>, <rs ref="#pmb44759" type="person">Göchhausen</rs>,
                     <rs type="person" ref="#pmb44760">Angelika Kauffmann</rs>. <rs type="work" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb46586">Aquarell</rs> v. <rs ref="#pmb44761" type="person">Schütz</rs>. (Schloss <rs type="place" ref="#pmb194">Tiefurt</rs>
                  bei <rs ref="#pmb197" type="place">Weimar</rs>.)</hi></p></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00043-B-00003-000-00022"/><rs ref="#pmb197" type="place">Weimar</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><date>1. III.</date></dateline></opener><p>Danke Ihnen, <salute>lieber Arthur,</salute><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehr für die lieben Zeilen (und wün<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>che
               mir<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehr mündlich weiteres). Wir<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ind <date>Montag</date> zurück und freuen uns auf
               Euch.</p><closer><signed>Hugo.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
